attributes.title: Trials HD
attributes.description: LtMkilla presents a new series for Achievement Hunter: Rage Quit. Each Thursday, let's journey through the trials and tribulations of his gaming highs and lows, mostly lows.

attributes.title: Superman Returns
attributes.description: LtMkilla is back and this time he takes on Superman Returns. What would you do if your car went missing

attributes.title: Super Meat Boy
attributes.description: LtMkilla takes a stab at Super Meat Boy, with hilarious and predictable results.

attributes.title: Ninja Gaiden 2
attributes.description: Mkilla plays Ninja Gaiden 2, and we laugh at his misery. It's the American way.

attributes.title: World at War
attributes.description: Mkill tries to win the war, by dodging one grenade at a time.

attributes.title: Fable 3
attributes.description: Rage Quit is back and it is ragier than ever! This time we follow LtMkilla and his pal as they play through Fable 3 and have a merry time. Enjoy!

attributes.title: The Impossible Game
attributes.description: LtMkilla takes a stab at the popular indie title "The Impossible Game" on Xbox Live Arcade.

attributes.title: Guitar Hero Metallica
attributes.description: LtMkilla tries his luck at online multiplayer in Guitar Hero: Metallica. Does he have what it takes

attributes.title: Bulletstorm
attributes.description: LtMkilla attempts to Kill With Skill in the newly released game Bulletstorm.

attributes.title: QWOP
attributes.description: Michael is back and bringing his RAGE to the most requested Rage Quit game ever, QWOP. Will he survive

attributes.title: N+
attributes.description: LtMkilla takes on another 360 arcade game. This time it's N+.

attributes.title: Apache Air Assault
attributes.description: Michael takes a stab at Apache Air Assault in this week's Rage Quit.

attributes.title: Ikaruga
attributes.description: Michael attempts to play Ikaruga in this very special edition of Ikaruga.

attributes.title: Crysis 2
attributes.description: Michael takes a trip through Crysis 2's airport security in this latest edition of Rage Quit.

attributes.title: Scott Pilgrim Vs. The World
attributes.caption: Scott Pilgrim vs the World
attributes.description: This week, Michael takes on Scott Pilgrim... wait, or does he take on the World Great. Now I'm confused.

attributes.title: Call of Duty: Black Ops - Call of the Dead
attributes.caption: Call of Duty: Black Ops - Call of the Dead
attributes.description: Michael fights off the hordes of undead in the new "Call of the Dead" DLC for Call of Duty: Black Ops.
attributes.display_title: Call of Duty: Black Ops - Call of the Dead

attributes.title: Yie Ar Kung-Fu
attributes.caption: Yie Ar Kung-Fu
attributes.description: LtMkilla takes a trip down memory lane to fight his way through the arcade classic Yie Ar Kung-Fu. I hope he brought enough quarters.

attributes.title: Brink
attributes.description: In this week's episode of Rage Quit, Michael takes a stab at playing Brink with bots. I think it might be time he take a stab at getting some friends to play online with.

attributes.title: Mortal Kombat
attributes.caption: Mortal Kombat
attributes.description: Michael throws down against Shao Kahn in Mortal Kombat for the Xbox 360.

attributes.title: Bangai-O HD: Missile Fury
attributes.caption: Bangai-O HD: Missile Fury
attributes.description: LtMkilla plays a game with "fury" in the title. This'll end well.

attributes.title: Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
attributes.caption: Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
attributes.description: Michael takes a trip down memory lane to attempt one of the hardest Achievements ever made in this week's Rage Quit.

attributes.title: Dead Rising 2
attributes.description: This week's Rage Quit is all that, and a bag of trash.

attributes.title: Scramble
attributes.caption: Scramble
attributes.description: LtMkilla takes on the arcade classic, Scramble, in this week's Rage Quit.

attributes.title: God of War 3
attributes.caption: God of War 3
attributes.description: In this week's Rage Quit, Michael enters uncharted (no pun intended) territory with God of War 3 and the PS3.

attributes.title: Rainbow Runner
attributes.caption: Rainbow Runner
attributes.description: This week, Michael takes on the indie darling "Rainbow Runner."

attributes.title: Duke Nukem Forever
attributes.caption: Duke Nukem Forever
attributes.description: Michael takes on the mini games in Duke Nukem Forever. Forget saving the Earth from an alien invasion, we've got Air Hockey and Pinball to play!

attributes.title: Ms. 'Splosion Man
attributes.caption: Ms. 'Splosion Man
attributes.description: If you've ever wondered if it's possible for LtMkilla to yell himself to death, this video might answer some questions, as he attempts Ms. 'Splosion Man.

attributes.title: X-Men Origins: Wolverine
attributes.caption: X-Men Origins: Wolverine
attributes.description: In this week's Rage Quit, Michael takes on Deadpool in the infamous final fight in X-Men Origins: Wolverine.

attributes.title: Perfect Dark
attributes.caption: Perfect Dark
attributes.description: Michael heads in to the world of Perfect Dark and hunts some AI. Or maybe it is the other way around.

attributes.title: Brave, A Warrior's Tale
attributes.caption: Brave, A Warrior's Tale
attributes.description: Michael does his best impression of Gollum in this week's edition of Rage Quit. Watch him face his worst enemy, laval, in Brave, A Warrior's Tale.

attributes.title: Catherine
attributes.caption: Catherine
attributes.description: Michael takes a big step in his growing process as he tackles Catherine. Will he fall in love (Spoiler: No.)

attributes.title: Behind the Rage
attributes.description: The cameras roll as Rage Quit records a new video.

attributes.title: Rezurrection
attributes.caption: Call of Duty: Black Ops
attributes.description: Michael flies himself to the Moon and takes on some zombies in another light-hearted family-friendly episode of Rage Quit. Call of Duty: Black Ops will never be the same after this Rezurrection DLC.

attributes.title: I Wanna Be The Guy
attributes.caption: I Wanna Be The Guy
attributes.description: Michael takes on a popular request, "I Wanna Be The Guy." Will he become the guy Spoiler: NO.

attributes.title: Resistance 3
attributes.caption: Resistance 3
attributes.description: Michael does his best to play Resistance 3. Well, he tries to at least.

attributes.title: Mutant Storm: Reloaded
attributes.caption: Mutant Storm: Reloaded
attributes.description: Michael takes his rage out on levels 64 and 65. Will he survive any level in Mutant Storm: Reloaded (Spoiler: Probably not.)

attributes.title: Gears of War 3 (HORDE Mode)
attributes.caption: Gears of War 3
attributes.description: Michael takes a stab at the last wave of HORDE mode in Gears of War 3. It goes about as well as you'd imagine.

attributes.title: Super Street Fighter 4
attributes.caption: Super Street Fighter 4
attributes.description: Michael picks the oldest character in the world and takes on Super Street Fighter 4. How do you think he'll do

attributes.title: Rage
attributes.caption: Rage
attributes.description: Michael takes on Rage in Rage Quit. Will he rage Better yet, how much will he Rage Will he Rage a lot Will he Rage a little Can he Rage while he Rages

attributes.title: Dark Souls
attributes.caption: Dark Souls
attributes.description: Michael takes a stab at one of the most anticipatedly difficult games this year: Dark Souls.

attributes.title: Behind the Rage Quit: QWOP
attributes.caption: QWOP
attributes.description: Today's special episode of Rage Quit is another look at one of the classics. Today you actually get to see Michael RAGE at QWOP. Enjoy this peek behind the scenes!

attributes.title: Battlefield 3
attributes.caption: Battlefield 3
attributes.description: In this very special episode of Rage Quit (by that I mean an episode with no game audio due to technical problems), Michael tries his hand at multiplayer in Battlefield 3. Will he carry his team to victory

attributes.title: Greg Hastings Paintball 2
attributes.caption: Greg Hastings Paintball 2
attributes.description: In this very special episode of Rage Quit, Michael tries his hand at Greg Hastings Paintball 2. Does he have what it takes to survive the mean streets of fake combat

attributes.title: Modern Warfare 3
attributes.caption: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3
attributes.description: Michael brings along Ray to complete this Rage Quit in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3. More like Modern WarFAIL 3, right Right

attributes.title: EA Sports MMA
attributes.caption: EA Sports MMA
attributes.description: This time anything goes when Michael and special guest Patrick Stewart throw down in EA Sports MMA. Age is just a number, right

attributes.title: Iron Man 2
attributes.caption: Iron Man 2
attributes.description: Michael suits up in this week's Rage Quit as he plays Iron Man 2. Do you think he has what it takes to be the man of steel No not that other guy, the one in the metal suit.

attributes.title: Homefront
attributes.caption: Homefront
attributes.description: This week on Rage Quit, Michael plays Homefront. Will he be able to lead the resistance to victory and reclaim America from North Korean occupation No, he won't.

attributes.title: Monopoly Streets
attributes.caption: Monopoly Streets
attributes.description: Michael returns to a simpler time on this week's Rage Quit with a gold old fashioned game of Monopoly Streets. Can he win it all or is bankruptcy in his future

attributes.title: Tetris Splash
attributes.caption: Tetris Splash
attributes.description: In this week's Rage Quit Michael dives into an underwater adventure as he plays Tetris Splash. I hope he brought enough oxygen.

attributes.title: Halo: Reach - LASO
attributes.caption: Halo: Reach
attributes.description: This week Michael tries his luck with the LASO (Legendary All Skulls On) challenge in Halo: Reach. I hope he doesn't mind adding one more skull to the collection, his.

attributes.title: Dodge 'Em
attributes.caption: Game Room - Dodge 'Em
attributes.description:
This week on Rage Quit Michael plays the Atari classic, Dodge 'Em.

Can he in fact, dodge them all No, he can't.
